description:
Create beautiful collages from your photos

If you love taking pictures of everything around you, then the best way to share it with your friends without disturbing them is to make a beautiful collage. With our Collagerator you can create a collage that collects favorite moments of your life.
Using Collagerator we can place 17 photos from a weekend in one picture. Or 22 photos from a wedding. Or 31 photos of a new born baby. Or... What can you do with it?
